          "plain_text": "This morning is even slower and I rise at 8am. The normal morning routine follows after that, changed only be a lot of reading. My body is feeling slow and sluggish today. Filen comments on the fact that the ocean drives the mood of people - the calm, quiet and still sea sets the tone. ",
          "href": null
        }
