          "plain_text": "Lorenzo, Dom and Jude walk off with their boards to Lwandile. I tell them that I will catch up with them and promise to bring my coffee making apparatus. The morning kind of runs away with me and my brother calls for a catchup. I call Jordan to her the tale of how she shaved her head and how she is doing - a cool head. ",
          "href": null
