          "plain_text": "I get two lefts at first that are rather average. The board is feeling really good though - it’s got about as much volume as Kim yet has a nose with a lot of rocker. It’s almost 20” wide yet feels like a high performance shortboard. I think that it would go really well in the tube with the quad fin setup. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
