            "content": "I talk Lorenzo through a game of backgammon and he picks it up quickly. I’m definitely becoming better at teaching people the game. We settle down around the fire that Lisa makes and I sink deep into the couch. I am about to play a game with Dom when Wayne and Pat walk in.",
